Post-Match Reflections: Georgia booked a place in the last 16 of Euro 2024 with a 2-0 win over Portugal
This was the biggest upset by FIFA rankings in European Championship history
Portugal's post-game interviews were interrupted as Tblisi celebrated the shock win
Miscellaneous Highlights: Match ended 2-0 in favor of Georgia
Georgia had 27.6% possession, while Portugal had 72.4%
Georgia took 3 shots on goal, compared to Portugal's 5
Georgia had 7 shot attempts, compared to Portugal's 22
Georgia received 1 yellow card, while Portugal received 3
Solomon Kverkvelia conceded a corner for Georgia
